1. Leaves uniform in color, red, pink, green to yellow-green, leaf base color not contrasting; limbidium at least partially bistratose, narrow; subalar auriculate inflated group of cells of fertile shoot leaves absent; costa percurrent to short-excurrent ........................ ......................................................................................................................................................................Subgenus 
